title: Maddie and Tae Update on Tae’s Baby and Her Sad Chicken Story +  Eddie Makes A Confession About the ‘Camp’ He Went To as A Kid + Update on Lunchbox’ Valentine’s Day Business
itunes:title: Maddie and Tae Update on Tae’s Baby and Her Sad Chicken Story +  Eddie Makes A Confession About the ‘Camp’ He Went To as A Kid + Update on Lunchbox’ Valentine’s Day Business
description:
We talk to Maddie of Maddie and Tae about their new album, get an update on Tae who just had a baby and get an unfortunate update on her chickens. Eddie reveals a key detail about the camp he went to as a kid where he met his friend “Jules” that he’s been trying to reunite with. Lunchbox gives us an update on whether or not he’s been able to sell any of the Valentine’s Day reservations he made as part of his business plan.
